      <hedline>
        <hl1>Warm and Serene</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Marie C Raisig letter on Jan 24 article hails return of wall-to-wall carpeting</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I'm so glad that wall-to-wall carpeting is again being favored by decorators. It creates the continuity, warmth and serenity we need, as bare wood cannot.</p>
        <p>MARIE C. RAISIG  Glen Cove, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
